我外出时喜欢做点事情。

299
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:55,800
I love the desert too, but the wilderness, somewhere where I'm outside.
我也喜欢沙漠，但荒野，那种户外的感觉。

300
00:15:55,800 --> 00:15:56,960
I live in a city.
我住在城市里。

301
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:57,960
I don't want to go to a city.
我不想去另一个城市。

302
00:15:57,960 --> 00:16:02,160
I like to go somewhere where I can walk around, hike, ride a bike, do things like that.
我喜欢去可以散步、徒步、骑自行车之类的地方。

303
00:16:02,160 --> 00:16:03,160
What about you?
你呢？

304
00:16:03,160 --> 00:16:07,840
I actually don't have a favorite, actually.
我其实没有特别喜欢的。

305
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,920
Sometimes it's nice for me to go to the beach and relax.
有时候去海滩放松一下也不错。

306
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:14,520
I do tend to get a little bit bored after maybe two days of doing nothing on the beach.
在海滩上无所事事两天后，我确实会有点无聊。

307
00:16:14,520 --> 00:16:18,720
But it does give a good opportunity to do other things, beach activities like snorkeling
但它也提供了做其他事情的好机会，比如海滩活动，像浮潜

308
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:22,160
or scuba diving, which can also be really fun.
或水肺潜水，这些也很有趣。

309
00:16:22,160 --> 00:16:30,560
But definitely I do enjoy the wilderness as well, the jungle and rafting or camping.
但当然我也喜欢荒野，丛林、漂流或露营。

310
00:16:30,560 --> 00:16:31,960
It's good fun.
很好玩。

311
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:36,000
The insects can be a bit of a nuisance at times.
昆虫有时候会有点烦人。

312
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,000
Or the rain.
或者下雨。

313
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,000
Or the rain.
或者下雨。

314
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:41,640
Getting in the snow or the rain is so horrible.
遇到雪或雨真是太糟糕了。

315
00:16:41,640 --> 00:16:42,880
But other than that, yeah, it's great.
但除此之外，是的，很棒。

316
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:49,000
I know not many people enjoy these types of outdoor getaways.
我知道不是很多人喜欢这种类型的户外度假。

317
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,880
But of course, you have spas.
但当然，还有水疗中心。

318
00:16:50,880 --> 00:16:53,840
I know many people enjoy going to a spa, having a mud bath.
我知道很多人喜欢去水疗中心，做泥浴。

319
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:55,400
Nothing wrong with that.
这没什么不好。

320
00:16:55,400 --> 00:16:57,920
Getting your nails done, having a massage.
做指甲、按摩。

321
00:16:57,920 --> 00:17:01,080
Getting the whole royal treatment, like we say.
享受全套皇家待遇，就像我们常说的那样。

322
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:04,040
So this is what we want to know now.
所以这就是我们现在想知道的。

323
00:17:04,040 --> 00:17:05,840
When you go on vacation, what do you like to do?
你去度假时，喜欢做什么？

324
00:17:05,840 --> 00:17:09,160
Do you like to get away to the tropical beaches?
你喜欢去热带海滩放松吗？

325
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:12,120
Do you like to go to the islands or the jungle?
你喜欢去岛屿还是丛林？

326
00:17:12,120 --> 00:17:13,120
What do you like to do?
你喜欢做什么？

327
00:17:13,120 --> 00:17:14,120
Let us know.
告诉我们吧。

328
00:17:14,120 --> 00:17:15,520
Our website is EnglishPod.com.
我们的网站是 EnglishPod.com。

329
00:17:15,520 --> 00:17:16,520
We hope to see you there.
我们希望能在那儿见到你。

330
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:17,520
All right.
好了。

331
00:17:17,520 --> 00:17:18,520
We'll see you guys next time.
我们下次再见。

332
00:17:18,520 --> 00:17:19,520
Bye.
拜拜。

333
00:17:19,520 --> 00:17:40,980
